Structured Query Language
It allows to define the structure of the database's relations e to control the access to the
database
edit the data contained in the databse, with insert, edit and delete
query the database

The table and the attributes of the table are called identifiers

The type of data could be:
BOOLEAN
CHARACTER(n)
DATE
TIME
INTEGER(p)
SMALLINT
INTEGER
DECIMAL(p,s)
REAL

where p indicate the maximum number of figures that can be contained
CHARACTER could be abbreviated with CHAR

An attribute is a column.
a record is a row containing data.
